    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "College is also involved in various activities and engaged students to improve their skills",
          "name": "Rating Sage",
          "course_tag_name": "BMS"
        },
        {
          "text": "College faculty and other supporting staff members are understanding and come with different curriculum",
          "name": "Rating Sage",
          "course_tag_name": "BMS"
        },
        {
          "text": "the canteen facility is great. you have variety of options from breakfast to lunch.",
          "name": "Rating Sage",
          "course_tag_name": "BMS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Faculties were good and understandable, good behaviour with students, teaching everything so we'll.",
          "name": "Review guru",
          "course_tag_name": "BMS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Sports like cricket football badminton boxing wrestling and many more,I took a part in football team",
          "name": "Review guru",
          "course_tag_name": "BMS"
        },
        {
          "text": "I liked the campus as it's so big and playground is available for any sports",
          "name": "Review guru",
          "course_tag_name": "BMS"
        },
        {
          "text": "The staff, teachers and overall management were too good, college had many facilities, and they used to take care of surrounding.",
          "name": "Kartik pawar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Traveling might be hectic as it's in the dadar area.",
          "name": "Review Ranger",
          "course_tag_name": "BMS"
        },
        {
          "text": "there is network issues sometimes in the campuse.",
          "name": "Rating Sage",
          "course_tag_name": "BMS"
        },
        {
          "text": "College canteen used to be affordable and so clean and good, but now they rebuilt it and it costs high price for every food item, for example a bowl of a maggie costs over 50rs",
          "name": "Review guru",
          "course_tag_name": "BMS"
        },
        {
          "text": "And other thing I disliked is that there's one supervisor in bms department,he's so rude ,his name is harshal adani, he doesn't understand students problem",
          "name": "Review guru",
          "course_tag_name": "BMS"
        },
        {
          "text": "What I disliked is that scholarship isn't available for higher caste students",
          "name": "Review guru",
          "course_tag_name": "BMS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Guards don't let students sit in the campus",
          "name": "Kartik pawar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Some of the classrooms are not clean at all",
          "name": "Kartik pawar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        }
      ]
    },
